WEBVTT

1
00:11:59.620 --> 00:12:02.260 
你气色这么好  让我很意外
but I'm just surprised at how well you look.

2
00:12:02.260 --> 00:12:04.870 
谢谢  其实我感觉很累
Oh, thank you, but I'm tired.

3
00:12:05.770 --> 00:12:09.230 
非常累  请坐  反正我需要坐下了
So very tired. Please sit. I know that I need to.

4
00:12:09.230 --> 00:12:11.650 
太奇怪了
Hmm, that's very odd.

5
00:12:11.650 --> 00:12:12.630 
怎么了
What?

6
00:12:12.630 --> 00:12:14.400 
你完全没有变瘸
You're not limping at all.

7
00:12:14.400 --> 00:12:15.760 
变瘸
Limping?

8
00:12:15.760 --> 00:12:17.600 
这个病的第一个症状就是变瘸
It's the first symptom of flett-giordano.

9
00:12:17.600 --> 00:12:20.840 
不好意思  我稍稍失陪一下
Would you just excuse me for just one moment?

10
00:12:29.270 --> 00:12:30.660 
爱尔卡人呢
Where's Elka?

